long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
If you love trivia and endless facts about the world, this extension is for you. DailyFactTab brings you a new, interesting fact about science, geography, nature, society and more each time you refresh or open a new Chrome tab. 

This extension includes a web search feature on the new tab which is powered by Yahoo!
